OFuz from source code
=====================

Introduction
------------
Ofuz is a platform for freelancer to manage Contacts, Tasks, Project and Invoices.
Clean un simplified user interface, it uses a concept of Co-Workers to work with other freelancers and customers on 
projects and client relations.

You can try it on our hosted version at:
http://www.ofuz.com/

An installable version is available at:
http://ofuz.com/opensource/

All questions will be answered on the forum
http://ofuz.com/opensource/forum/


Source code on GITHub
------

The source code is hosted on GitHub
https://github.com/philfree/ofuz

To get the source code version working we have instructions in the wiki
http://ofuz.com/opensource/wiki/


